Orpea SA,  France ’s largest
commercial retirement-home operator, said first-quarter
sales rose 27 percent to 293 million euros.  The company confirmed its 2011 revenue target of more
than 1.21 billion euros in a statement in  Les Echos .  ALL TIMES CET  WHAT TO WATCH:
